%p
  Here's how we interpreted the reference:
%ul
  %li
    %span House:
    = @reference.house
  %li
    %span Date:
    = @reference.date_to_s
  - if @reference.volume
    %li
      %span Volume:
      = @reference.volume
  - if @reference.column
    %li
      %span Start column:
      = @reference.column
  -if @reference.sitting_type
    %li
      %span Type:
      = @reference.sitting_type

%p
  Either we don't have that Hansard in our database, or there is no Hansard that matches the reference:
%ul
  %li
    = @query
%p
  Try browsing our
  %a{:href => "#{request.host}/sittings/#{@reference.year}"}= "sittings in #{@reference.year}"